Nancy Dow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nancy_Dow 0 Nancy Maryanne Dow (July 22, 1936 – May 25, 2016) was an American actress and model who appeared in a brief group of films and television shows. She was married to actor John Aniston with whom she had a daughter, actress Jennifer Aniston.
